{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"新中国颂歌","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":1}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有是被批"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准的！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立了中华人民共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不曾幻想也根本不要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动派来举手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义来祝贺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天是人民开的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地是人民辟的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺回自己手创的江山有权利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让敌人看着罢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在九百五十九万七千方公里的东半球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四万万七千五百万中国人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了自己的共和国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那个强盗敢来动撼我们土地上的一棵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾以自己的枪刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫了我们的版图！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是有骨气的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有那些汉奸、卖国贼、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才递降表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设喜筵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"致欢迎辞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让蒋介石的宪法引火罢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让帝国主义制定的法律包口红罢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照蒋介石的宪法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照帝国主义制定的法律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民只配做奴隶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国只配做殖民地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但我们是主人了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们挣脱了一切铐镣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界也最欢乐；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们自己在鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们自己在欢呼歌唱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的人民也都在为我们鼓掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的人民也都在为我们欢呼歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决定了自己的运命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们壮大了世界的民主阵营！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国亮了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界的东方也亮了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国是张灯结采的中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界是欢腾鼓舞的世界。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战战兢兢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门庭冷落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车马稀零，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是当然的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一定的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正因为这样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们更欢乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是近百年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是中国人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争的成果；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是马克思、恩格斯、列宁、斯大林、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和毛泽东的思想的成果。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的历史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要写着毛泽东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界的历史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要写着毛泽东；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国的历史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要写着我们粗手大脚的工人和农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界的历史上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要写着我们粗手大脚的工人和农民的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让“白皮书”象死了妈样的哭泣罢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让杜鲁门、马歇尔、艾奇逊、邱吉尔、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁托们抖得拢做一团罢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让“希特勒传”包油条罢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让“总裁言论集”擦屁股罢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那些捏造的历史和年谱都翻过案来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接着中国的十月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接着中华人民共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最欢乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们比苏联建设得要快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们比苏联的条件更好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有苏联！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天人民的日本、朝鲜、印度、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和一切被压迫的人民的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比中国和苏联建设得更要快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比中国和苏联的条件要更好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经有了苏联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了新民主各国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更有了我们中华人民共和国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自己的祖国的红旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在毛泽东的面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象百鸟朝凤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象大海沸腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了胜利；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真正的有了自己的中华人民共和国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向世界人民发出友好的电告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的国家成立了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从苦难中站起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要和兄弟们永远在一起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫我们的世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫我们自己！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向蒋介石发去通牒："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就消灭！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向帝国主义者们警告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“谁的血爪敢伸进中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁的血爪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要被砍掉！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向地主、特务、反动分子下命令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“捣乱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要治罪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不自新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"………………”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民要向毛泽东宣誓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向世界宣誓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着你——毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远倒在苏联这一边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们爱我们的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象爱自己的生命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要建设这国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的工厂的烟囱都要冒烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的矿山都要辟开来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的土地要长出好庄稼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要征服一切天灾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要象扑蝗除虫一样把它消灭！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要成为一块干净的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要成为一块劳动的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要成为一块丰收的土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要成为一块英雄的土地！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}